1
00:00:03,340 --> 00:00:09,180
♪You're the unattainable star♪

2
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:14,940
♪I'm the tiniest dust in the world♪

3
00:00:15,020 --> 00:00:17,820
♪With all the sincerity I can muster♪

4
00:00:18,020 --> 00:00:20,860
♪For your kiss after the tears♪

5
00:00:20,980 --> 00:00:23,100
♪Through the storm♪

6
00:00:23,220 --> 00:00:27,180
♪I'd like to travel with you♪

7
00:00:28,940 --> 00:00:30,370
[Beauty Strategy Season 1]

8
00:00:30,370 --> 00:00:34,980
[Adapted from The Spirit Queen
by TUTU on Kuaikan Comic]

9
00:00:34,980 --> 00:00:37,980
[Episode 20]
[Who Exterminated the Spirit Clan?]

10
00:00:51,140 --> 00:00:52,700
Did you seal my memories?

11
00:00:53,780 --> 00:00:55,140
You unsealed them?

12
00:00:57,860 --> 00:00:58,460
I...

13
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:01,660
I got back some of them.

14
00:01:01,780 --> 00:01:02,700
But tell me.

15
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:04,940
What on earth happened six years ago?

16
00:01:05,220 --> 00:01:06,180
Did the slaughter of the Spirit clan

17
00:01:06,980 --> 00:01:08,340
have something to do with me?

18
00:01:14,420 --> 00:01:15,460
Don't guess wildly.

19
00:01:16,940 --> 00:01:17,820
The slaughter of your clan

20
00:01:19,100 --> 00:01:19,820
had nothing to do with you.

21
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:22,060
You're still lying.

22
00:01:23,780 --> 00:01:24,420
Bingjian,

23
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:26,180
I beg you.

24
00:01:26,980 --> 00:01:28,580
Unseal all my memories.

25
00:01:37,540 --> 00:01:38,180
Shuoye!

26
00:01:39,460 --> 00:01:41,020
Those memories will only
give you more pain.

27
00:01:41,980 --> 00:01:43,020
Since you've lost them,

28
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:44,940
why must you dwell on the past?

29
00:01:53,220 --> 00:01:54,020
Pain?

30
00:01:55,460 --> 00:01:57,340
Will I feel no pain

31
00:01:57,980 --> 00:01:59,220
when I'm kept in the dark?

32
00:02:06,460 --> 00:02:08,460
At least, you're alive now.

33
00:02:10,540 --> 00:02:12,220
I just want you to be alive.

34
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:22,460
These memories...

35
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:24,700
may give me either pain

36
00:02:25,620 --> 00:02:26,580
or embarrassment.

37
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:28,860
They're part of me.

38
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:32,540
I'm no longer what I was six years ago.

39
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,260
I won't tell you.

40
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:38,020
You should go.

41
00:02:38,740 --> 00:02:39,580
Even if you hate me,

42
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:40,860
I won't let you

43
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:42,500
experience the pain of despair again.

44
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:45,340
I saw that.

45
00:02:46,380 --> 00:02:48,700
It was Mu Xuanjue
who killed my clansmen.

46
00:02:50,420 --> 00:02:54,060
I should hate no one but him.

47
00:02:56,980 --> 00:02:57,740
Shuoye.

48
00:03:03,350 --> 00:03:05,230
♪Falling into a story♪

49
00:03:05,990 --> 00:03:09,150
♪I disturbed a dream♪

50
00:03:10,310 --> 00:03:12,390
♪I used to be a speck of dust♪

51
00:03:13,070 --> 00:03:15,950
♪Involved in delusion♪

52
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:19,950
♪If the illusion of life♪

53
00:03:21,350 --> 00:03:23,150
♪Was sealed in time♪

54
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:25,340
♪I'd wake up from obsession♪

55
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:25,940
What?

56
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:27,780
You seem

57
00:03:28,980 --> 00:03:30,340
to be interested in the sword.

58
00:03:31,550 --> 00:03:33,550
♪Grass always faded silently♪

59
00:03:34,230 --> 00:03:36,670
♪With no one knowing that♪

60
00:03:37,660 --> 00:03:38,860
This sword is extremely sharp.

61
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:40,500
It even cuts hair easily.

62
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:42,540
Don't hurt yourself.

63
00:03:42,540 --> 00:03:44,350
♪Rooted deeper♪

64
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:48,230
♪If love had never♪

65
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:51,390
♪Broken into my heart♪

66
00:03:51,830 --> 00:03:54,350
♪When I looked back, I'd miss♪

67
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:58,070
♪Who I met at first sight♪

68
00:03:58,350 --> 00:04:01,870
♪I kept dreaming about you♪

69
00:04:02,070 --> 00:04:05,150
♪But I had to sleep alone♪

70
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:07,190
♪I'd forget♪

71
00:04:07,270 --> 00:04:11,790
♪All the miserable old memories♪

72
00:04:12,510 --> 00:04:16,630
♪Expecting to get wet
in the snow when I'm old♪

73
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:19,880
♪I'll turn around for my next life♪

74
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:21,640
♪If I'm lucky enough
to grow old with you♪

75
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:26,480
♪How much will destiny
keep its promise?♪

76
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:31,420
I think you love this sword.

77
00:04:33,020 --> 00:04:34,060
This sword...

78
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:37,020
You have used it for a long time, right?

79
00:04:37,460 --> 00:04:40,300
When I was 16, the late Emperor

80
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:42,220
gave this sword to me.

81
00:04:42,940 --> 00:04:44,100
I've been using it
for nearly a decade.

82
00:04:45,460 --> 00:04:49,180
How many people
of my clan did you kill with it?

83
00:04:56,900 --> 00:04:57,740
Calm down.

84
00:04:58,260 --> 00:04:59,020
Back then,

85
00:04:59,380 --> 00:05:01,380
you were the one
who led the army to fight my clan,

86
00:05:01,980 --> 00:05:02,940
Mu Xuanjue!

87
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:04,260
You've recalled it?

88
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:06,300
Today,

89
00:05:06,980 --> 00:05:09,180
I'll make you pay for my clansmen.

90
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:48,340
He was indeed sent by Her Majesty.

91
00:06:13,690 --> 00:06:15,100
♪My eyebrows are outlined
against the rain♪

92
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:16,060
Mu Xuanjue,

93
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:18,860
exterminating my clan
made you my sworn enemy.

94
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:22,020
Today, I'll make you pay with your life!

95
00:06:22,020 --> 00:06:24,050
♪The wind sighs softly at our destiny♪

96
00:06:24,410 --> 00:06:26,140
♪Love and hate are forever gone♪

97
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:27,100
In that war,

98
00:06:28,580 --> 00:06:30,780
I was appointed as the vanguard.

99
00:06:31,700 --> 00:06:33,860
But I didn't kill even a single member

100
00:06:33,860 --> 00:06:34,780
of your clan.

101
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:37,500
Please trust me.

102
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,580
Say no more.

103
00:06:39,660 --> 00:06:41,180
I won't believe you.

104
00:06:42,340 --> 00:06:44,420
I only believe what I saw.

105
00:06:44,420 --> 00:06:46,570
♪If I can be greedy♪

106
00:06:46,970 --> 00:06:50,330
♪You will be what I want for this life♪

107
00:06:50,970 --> 00:06:53,970
♪Yet you don't even look back
when the song ends♪

108
00:06:54,290 --> 00:06:57,610
♪Who gets stuck in the dream with me?♪

109
00:06:57,810 --> 00:07:01,290
♪Old memories never yield♪

110
00:07:01,490 --> 00:07:03,100
♪Under the spring breeze,
the flowers bloom as before♪

111
00:07:03,100 --> 00:07:05,020
You think I'm your enemy
who massacred your clansmen, right?

112
00:07:05,860 --> 00:07:06,620
What?

113
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:08,420
You can't bear to hurt me?

114
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:09,780
No.

115
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:11,540
Then kill me.

116
00:07:12,810 --> 00:07:17,170
♪The moonlight gently falls
into your eyes♪

117
00:07:17,210 --> 00:07:20,250
♪The gentle smell lingers♪

118
00:07:20,370 --> 00:07:23,970
♪How can I stay with this beauty?♪

119
00:07:24,090 --> 00:07:27,730
♪I don't know and I can't help crying♪

120
00:07:27,850 --> 00:07:32,170
♪The smile looks so familiar♪

121
00:07:32,290 --> 00:07:34,020
♪Like the running stream♪

122
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:34,820
Lingzhi,

123
00:07:36,180 --> 00:07:37,500
it's all right
that you don't believe me.

124
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:40,660
But I'll prove everything to you.

125
00:07:40,660 --> 00:07:42,690
♪Happy or sad, do not look back♪

126
00:07:42,850 --> 00:07:46,090
♪I smile and ask about it♪

127
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:00,900
Consort Huan?

128
00:08:01,540 --> 00:08:02,820
I thought you were dead.

129
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:06,300
Mu Xuanjue,

130
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:09,660
are you going to execute me
in front of your beloved

131
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:11,700
to make her happy?

132
00:08:34,620 --> 00:08:35,300
Saya,

133
00:08:36,260 --> 00:08:37,420
the palace isn't a good place
for you to stay.

134
00:08:37,900 --> 00:08:38,620
Go home.

135
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:41,380
Will you really not kill me?

136
00:08:42,540 --> 00:08:43,700
I've never meant to kill you.

137
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:45,860
All this time,

138
00:08:46,180 --> 00:08:48,100
I've only wanted to force you
to leave and go home.

139
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:49,340
But...

140
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:52,820
Only when Her Majesty
believes you're dead

141
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:54,780
can we deceive everyone.

142
00:08:55,460 --> 00:08:58,900
The Mu Xuanjue I know
can't be so kind-hearted.

143
00:09:02,380 --> 00:09:05,180
Tell me. What do you want?

144
00:09:05,860 --> 00:09:07,340
I really want you to do something.

145
00:09:07,980 --> 00:09:09,660
Take one thing back to your clan for me.

146
00:09:11,980 --> 00:09:12,700
I knew it.

147
00:09:14,180 --> 00:09:15,620
You would never make a bad deal.

148
00:09:16,380 --> 00:09:17,380
What do you want me to take back?

149
00:09:20,700 --> 00:09:21,700
Your story.

150
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:26,180
To flatter the Human clan's
imperial family,

151
00:09:26,580 --> 00:09:27,940
the Sun General of the Phantom clan

152
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:29,780
was sent to the palace
by the nobles of her clan

153
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:31,420
and became Consort Huan.

154
00:09:32,020 --> 00:09:33,780
Consort Huan suffered all kinds
of humiliation in the palace.

155
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:36,900
Finally, she had a narrow escape
back to her clan.

156
00:09:39,500 --> 00:09:41,220
Through your story,

157
00:09:41,620 --> 00:09:43,100
I want to tell your clansmen

158
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:45,060
that flattery can't
get respect for them.

159
00:09:46,020 --> 00:09:48,100
You should lead them
to fight against Her Majesty.

160
00:09:50,940 --> 00:09:51,700
Only in this way

161
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:55,020
can we become a real alliance.

162
00:10:03,380 --> 00:10:04,100
This sword...

163
00:10:04,740 --> 00:10:07,460
Give it back to me
after we defeat Her Majesty.

164
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:42,760
♪My eyebrows are outlined
against the rain♪

165
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:46,500
♪Lovesickness tastes like bitter wine♪

166
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:50,200
♪The wind sighs softly at our destiny♪

167
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:53,840
♪Love and hate are forever gone♪

168
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:57,640
♪Don't ask where I'm going♪

169
00:10:58,080 --> 00:11:01,280
♪I won't change my love for you♪

170
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:05,000
♪My destination is my fate,
my obsession is to wait♪

171
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:09,080
♪I'm just destined to wander♪

172
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:12,760
♪If I can be greedy♪

173
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:16,480
♪You will be what I want for this life♪

174
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:20,200
♪Yet you don't even look back
when the song ends♪

175
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:23,960
♪Who gets stuck in the dream with me?♪

176
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:27,520
♪Old memories never yield♪

177
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:31,360
♪Under the spring breeze,
the flowers bloom as before♪

178
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:35,040
♪When clouds are dispersed,
I will disappear♪

179
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:38,400
♪However far away I stay,
I'm always who I am♪

180
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,730
♪The moonlight gently falls♪
